snapshot.description:

Definition of Done:

    Deploy the code into a container.

Acceptance criteria:

    Write a dockerfile for the project
    Build a docker image using the docker file

content:
**SPRINT 1:**

**Sprint 1 Planning :**

_Sprint goal:_ Set up the code-base and microservice for Taiga integration.

**Sprint Review :**

**Sprint Retrospective**

**Minutes of Standups:**

**SPRINT 1:**

**Sprint 1 Planning :**

_Sprint goal:_ Set up the code-base and microservice for Taiga integration.

**Sprint Review  :**

We are a team which interacts with the Taiga API, no other team has to do that, we filter the data and provide the teams with respective fields they need and ask for.

So no video demo.

**Sprint Retrospective:** 

![](https://media-protected.taiga.io/attachments/8/9/b/b/8efb98270b0d16037a64c49d160b1d1aff7bb72d8b3ed016b606ff8be51e/image.png?token=YkqGaA%3A02IWFme7jrfNH5YIq0ZwLs5sb_P047ve2mALNHkE2t_V25QgTyDS51x0Kvjbfq3uDTZTsiDr3wY5RxGNQl7uvg#_taiga-refresh=wikipage:1580074)

**What went well:**

*   Setting up codebase using Java-Maven
*   Since we were able to close 79% of the stories and couldn't close only 1 User Story. We can conclude tat we could achieve most of our sprint goal.
*   Additionally, we could provide 2 teams with the Taiga data for their metric calculation for Sprint1.
*   We did a good job of constant communicating with other teams about their requirements.

**What could have been better:**

*   We started off late were able to pick it up during the mid to end phase.
*   We couldn't close User story of deploying the containers for the microservice.
*   Team communication was lacking.

**What we will change for the next sprint:**

*   Deliver value at a constant pace from start.

**Minutes of Standups:**

**03/28/21**

*   Revised on the technical stack and requirements to start
*   Revised on user stories based on requirements

**03/30/21**

*   Started working on the base structure of the code
*   Decided on how to write a docker file for the Maven-based application
*   Decided on what Taiga endpoints to hit for the required data.

**03/31/21**

*   Working on fetching happiness factor for the other Team requirement
*   Also working on fetch tasks status for CFD metric
